# Images Directory

Generated promotional images for ElBruno.OllamaMonitor will be stored here.

See `image-prompts.md` for detailed prompts to generate these images.

## Planned Images

- `ollama-monitor-blog-hero.png` — Blog post hero image
- `ollama-monitor-linkedin.png` — LinkedIn social media image
- `ollama-monitor-twitter.png` — Twitter/X image
- `ollama-monitor-square.png` — Square social media image
- `ollama-monitor-logo.png` — App logo (256×256, 512×512)
- `ollama-monitor-in-action.png` — Screenshot showing app in use
- `ollama-monitor-banner.png` — Promotional banner
- `ollama-monitor-icon-states.png` — Icon states showcase

## How to Generate

1. Use a text-to-image tool (DALL-E, Midjourney, Stable Diffusion, etc.)
2. Copy prompts from `image-prompts.md`
3. Generate and save images here with appropriate filenames
4. Commit images to the repository

For more details, see [Image Prompts](image-prompts.md).
